data.description: GOLF COURSE VIEW HOME! Welcome to the beautiful Sun City Palm Desert 55+ gated golf course community!  Must see this beautiful "Emerald" floor plan!  As you enter the home through the double door entry, you have a large formal living room and dining area with golf course and mountain views, then to a large spacious kitchen with a large island with an eat at bar, an abundance of countertop and cabinet space plus a breakfast nook area. The spacious family room is open to the kitchen and creates a "great room" concept.  Off the formal living room area there is a spacious office/den with an attached half bathroom.  The large primary suite has beautiful golf course and mountain views, large primary bathroom with dual sinks, step in shower, large soaking tub, and a large walk in closet. Laundry room has a folding table, sink and extra cabinets for storage.   Spacious 2.5 car garage, perfect for 2 cars plus an area for golf cart/workshop/extra storage! Gated front yard with fruit trees. Southeast facing backyard is amazing with endless golf course and mountain views, a large alumawood covered patio, and low maintenance landscaping.
